This is a Black Highlighter-based theme by [[*user EstrellaYoshte]], derived from the visuals of [[[SCP-5999|]]].

You will need to import the Black Highlighter theme as well in order to use this theme. To learn more, go [[[theme:black-highlighter-theme|here]]].

**To import this theme, simply add the following to your page:**

> @@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:black-highlighter-theme]]@@
> @@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:isolated-terminal]]@@

